net.enilink.composition.properties.annotations

  • Packages that use net.enilink.composition.properties.annotations 
    Package Description
    net.enilink.vocab.owl
    This file specifies in RDF Schema format the built-in classes and properties that together form the basis of the RDF/XML syntax of OWL Full, OWL DL and OWL Lite.
    net.enilink.vocab.rdfs

  • Classes in net.enilink.composition.properties.annotations used by net.enilink.vocab.owl 
    Class and Description
    Type
    Methods with this annotation will use the configured type instead of the actual return type of the method.
  • Classes in net.enilink.composition.properties.annotations used by net.enilink.vocab.rdfs 
    Class and Description
    Localized
    Methods with this annotation will use the configured locale to use the closest matching or the set of closest matching String values.
